### 5.1 Amplification
Awareness intensifies along a gradient.

### 5.2 Suppression
Awareness weakens along a gradient.

### 5.3 Drift
Awareness moves unpredictably.

### 5.4 Stabilization
Awareness becomes steady.

### 5.5 Collapse
Awareness loses direction entirely.

Dynamics determine insight stability.

